      *@   보증금액　및　대출잔액（한도）원화　환산
      *    간접익스포져　명목액　산출－보증사유에따라　금액　산출
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3620-SELECT-GANJAN-RTN.

      * 명목금액，한도금액，잔액중　어느금액으로　익스포져산출할것인가
      *       통화코드
      *     　통화설정금액
      *     　원화환산금액
      *     　간접익스포져명목액적용율（１．０／１．３）

      *   통화코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-CNCYCD
             TO  WK-TONGCD

      *   통화설정금액
           MOVE  WK-H-O-SETAMT
             TO  WK-JANNEK

      * 1.담보설정금액　원화환산
           IF  WK-H-O-CNCYCD = CO-CHA-KRW
      *        통화코드
                MOVE  WK-H-O-CNCYCD
                  TO  WK-TP1-TONGCD

      *        통화설정금액
                MOVE  WK-H-O-SETAMT
                  TO  WK-TP1-JANNEK

      *        원화환산금액
                MOVE  WK-H-O-SETAMT
                  TO  WK-TP1-WONGK

           ELSE
      *       통화별　원화환산금액CALCURATER
               PERFORM  S3621-BJLTGEX-CALL-RTN
                  THRU  S3621-BJLTGEX-CALL-EXT

      *        통화코드
                MOVE  WK-TONGCD
                  TO  WK-TP1-TONGCD

      *        통화설정금액
                MOVE  WK-JANNEK
                  TO  WK-TP1-JANNEK

      *        원화환산금액
                MOVE  WK-WONGK
                  TO  WK-TP1-WONGK
           END-IF


      * 2.한도／잔액　원화환산
           INITIALIZE    WK-TONGCD
                         WK-JANNEK
                         WK-WONGK

      *   통화코드
           MOVE  WK-TMP-CNCYCD
             TO  WK-TONGCD

      *   통화설정금액
           MOVE  WK-TMP-CNPR-BAL
             TO  WK-JANNEK

           IF  WK-TONGCD = CO-CHA-KRW
      *        통화코드
                MOVE  WK-TMP-CNCYCD
                  TO  WK-TP2-TONGCD

      *        통화설정금액
                MOVE  WK-TMP-CNPR-BAL
                  TO  WK-TP2-JANNEK

      *        원화환산금액
                MOVE  WK-TMP-CNPR-BAL
                  TO  WK-TP2-WONGK
           ELSE
      *       통화별　원화환산금액CALCURATER
               PERFORM  S3621-BJLTGEX-CALL-RTN
                  THRU  S3621-BJLTGEX-CALL-EXT

      *        통화코드
                MOVE  WK-TONGCD
                  TO  WK-TP2-TONGCD

      *        통화설정금액
                MOVE  WK-JANNEK
                  TO  WK-TP2-JANNEK

      *        원화환산금액
                MOVE  WK-WONGK
                  TO  WK-TP2-WONGK
           END-IF

      * 보증사유－책임준공／자금보충이면　명목액＝금액／１．０　적용
      * 기타사유－　　　　　　　　　　　　명목액＝금액／１．３　적용
      * 보증사유－２２，２３，２４，２５－＞２７，２８，２９，３０

140530* 담보설정비율구분
      *  1: 130%(1.3)   2:120%(1.2)  3:110%(1.1)  4:160%(1.6) 그외 1.3

      *  설정금액 = 보증금액 ÷ 보증대상금액비율
      *  (상품코드:00018,00019,00020,00021는 1.0 으로 나눔)


           EVALUATE  WK-H-O-SCURTY-S-RATO-DSTCD
               WHEN  '1'
                     MOVE  1.3  TO  WK-SCURTY-S-RATO
               WHEN  '2'
                     MOVE  1.2  TO  WK-SCURTY-S-RATO
               WHEN  '3'
                     MOVE  1.1  TO  WK-SCURTY-S-RATO
               WHEN  '4'
                     MOVE  1.6  TO  WK-SCURTY-S-RATO
               WHEN  OTHER
140818               MOVE  1.3  TO  WK-SCURTY-S-RATO
           END-EVALUATE

           INITIALIZE  WK-DIVIDE

           IF ( RJL0027-PRDCT-NO = '00018' OR
                RJL0027-PRDCT-NO = '00019' OR
                RJL0027-PRDCT-NO = '00020' OR
                RJL0027-PRDCT-NO = '00021')
           THEN
                MOVE  1.0               TO  WK-DIVIDE
           ELSE
140530          MOVE  WK-SCURTY-S-RATO  TO  WK-DIVIDE
           END-IF

           IF WK-DIVIDE = CO-NUM-0
           THEN
      *       통화코드
               MOVE  SPACE
                 TO  RJL0027-CNCYCD
      *       통화설정금액
               MOVE  ZERO
                 TO  RJL0027-CRNCY-SETAMT
      *       원화환산금액
               MOVE  ZERO
                 TO  RJL0027-WONC-AUC
      *       간접명목금액
               MOVE  ZERO
                 TO  RJL0027-INDR-TTL-AMT
           ELSE

               INITIALIZE  WK-IMSI-AMT
               COMPUTE   WK-IMSI-AMT
                     =   WK-TP1-WONGK / WK-DIVIDE

               IF  WK-IMSI-AMT > WK-TP2-WONGK
               THEN

      *          통화코드
                  MOVE  WK-TP2-TONGCD
                    TO  RJL0027-CNCYCD
      *          통화설정금액
                  MOVE  WK-TP2-JANNEK
                    TO  RJL0027-CRNCY-SETAMT
      *          원화환산금액
                  MOVE  WK-TP2-WONGK
                    TO  RJL0027-WONC-AUC
      *          간접명목금액
                  MOVE  WK-TP2-WONGK
                    TO  RJL0027-INDR-TTL-AMT

               ELSE

      *          통화코드
                  MOVE  WK-TP1-TONGCD
                    TO  RJL0027-CNCYCD
      *          통화설정금액
                  MOVE  WK-TP1-JANNEK
                    TO  RJL0027-CRNCY-SETAMT
      *          원화환산금액
                  MOVE  WK-TP1-WONGK
                    TO  RJL0027-WONC-AUC
      *          간접명목금액
                  MOVE  WK-IMSI-AMT
                    TO  RJL0027-INDR-TTL-AMT
      *           명목액원천구분- 1:설정금액
                  MOVE  'THKIE0436-1'
                    TO   WK-GUBUN
               END-IF
           END-IF
           .
       S3620-SELECT-GANJAN-EXT.
           EXIT.
